title: BelowDeckMed: These Are The Daves of Our Lives
description: Dave and Natasha try to keep their relationship under wraps on Below Deck Mediterranean, but the rest of the yentas on board know something's up. Meanwhile, Raygan proves to be as good a dancer as she is a bosun.
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
